trans-unit.source: Use Bearer Authentication (recommended): Use a Token for Bearer Authentication (RFC 6750) and API key instead of the standard e-mail address and API key.
trans-unit.target: Use Bearer Authentication (recommended): Use a Token for Bearer Authentication (RFC 6750) and API key instead of the standard e-mail address and API key.

trans-unit.source: Email: The e-mail address associated with the API key.
trans-unit.target: E-mail: E-mailadressen i forbindelse med API-nøglen.

trans-unit.source: API Key: This is the API key made available on your account page (https://dash.cloudflare.com/profile)
trans-unit.target: API-nøgle: Dette er den API-nøgle, der gøres tilgængelig på din kontoside (https://dash.cloudflare.com/profile)

trans-unit.source: Domains: Please tick the domains whose cache should be flushed on Cloudflare upon clearing all caches in TYPO3.
trans-unit.target: Domæner: Sæt kryds i de domæner, hvis cache skal ryddes på Cloudflare ved sletning af alle caches i TYPO3.

trans-unit.source: Enable Analytics Backend module: Tick this checkbox if you need the Analytics module in Backend (this requires proper Token permissions if using Bearer Authentication).
trans-unit.target: Aktiv+er Analytics Backend modulet: Markér dette afkrydsningsfelt, hvis du har brug for Analytics modulet i Backend (dette kræver korrekte token tilladelser hvis du bruger Bearer Authentication).

trans-unit.source: Originating IPs: Tick this checkbox in case you cannot restore the originating IPs at the webserver level.
trans-unit.target: Oprindelige IP'er: Markér dette afkrydsningsfelt, hvis du ikke kan gendanne de oprindelige IP'er på webserverniveau.

trans-unit.source: [EXPERIMENTAL] Purge individual files by URL: Granularly remove individual files from Cloudflare's cache by specifying the URL. BEWARE: Highly experimental!
trans-unit.target: [EXPERIMENTAL] Ryd individuelle filer fra URL: Fjern Granulerede individuelle filer fra Cloudflare's cache ved at angive URL. PAS PÅ: Meget eksperimentelt!

trans-unit.source: Purge cache by Cache-Tag: Granularly remove individual files from Cloudflare's cache by specifying the associated Cache-Tag. BEWARE: This option requires an Enterprise account.
trans-unit.target: Ryd cache via Cache-Tag: Fjern granulerede individuelle filer fra Cloudflare's cache ved at angive den tilknyttede Cache-Tag. PAS PÅ: Denne indstilling kræver en Enterprise-konto.

trans-unit.source: Empty list fetched from Cloudflare, please check your credentials.
trans-unit.target: Tom liste hentet fra Cloudflare, tjek venligst dine legitimationsoplysninger.
